            . I live at No. 10, Goswell-street, and am a pawnbroker. On Tuesday, the 8th of February, the prisoner came to my shop about eight o'clock in the evening; he offered this spoon to pawn, and I detained him.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 12.</p>
